        "description": "<p>WordPress does not allow upload ePUB and MOBI formats.<br />\nThis plugin will enable the uploading of ePUB and MOBI files.</p>\n<h4>Social Media</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/eKnizky/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Like Us</a> on Facebook and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/eKnizky\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">follow us</a> on Twitter.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Go to plugins in your dashboard and select &#8216;add new&#8217;</li>\n<li>Search for &#8216;Allow ePUB and MOBI formats upload&#8217; </li>\n<li>Click &#8216;Install Now&#8217; and then activate the plugin</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<p>Our support forum is available on <a href=\"https://eknizky.sk/diskusia/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">support</a> website.</p>\n",
